# mdBook build output.
book/

# Copied-in chapters under src/ (SSOT is .omne/cfg/*.md when available,
# docs/src-authored/*.md otherwise; docs/build.{sh,ps1} regenerates these and
# prepends an AUTO-GENERATED banner at build time). Ignore every src/*.md,
# then re-include the authored pages (SUMMARY.md, introduction.md,
# pack-template.md). `docs/src-authored/*.md` is the git-tracked fallback —
# not gitignored here.
src/*.md
!src/SUMMARY.md
!src/introduction.md
!src/pack-template.md
